---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Research Papers | EES"
  description="Published findings from our thermal comfort, radiant conditioning, and energy efficiency research."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Research Papers</h1>
      <p>Published findings from our thermal comfort and energy research.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Our Research</h2>
      <p>
        Our research focuses on radiant conditioning, thermal comfort, hydronic systems, and net-zero building strategies. We publish our findings to contribute to industry knowledge and validate our product development.
      </p>

      <h3>Research Areas</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Thermal comfort evaluation (ASHRAE-55 / ISO 7730)</li>
        <li>Radiant ceiling panel performance</li>
        <li>Polyvalent heat pump efficiency</li>
        <li>Renewable energy integration for grid independence</li>
        <li>Staged approaches to net-zero buildings</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Papers &amp; Publications</h2>
      <p><em>Papers and publications will be listed here. Please check back soon or <a href="/contact">contact us</a> for direct access to our research.</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
